'''Vape charges''' were the [[Chiss/Legends|Chiss]] equivalent of the [[Thermal detonator/Legends|thermal detonator]] and, similarly to it, it used a [[Baradium/Legends|baradium]] charge to destroy its target. They were known to disintegrate anything within its blast radius and left nothing behind as evidence.

[[Chiss commando|Chiss Commandos]] were known to use vape charges for demolition operations against enemy targets.

